{"tid":2205829,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"尖沙嘴舊樓蝕近五千萬放售","createTime":"2020-09-17T05:47:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-17T05:47:14.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"2c13f1cfe06bd23e2005beeb15887923ab704d6c","tid":2205829,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T05:47:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20200917/OW6MAMN4IZDIDFXDYWHRKITFLY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200917%2FOW6MAMN4IZDIDFXDYWHRKITFLY%2F&d=WBhgCLuhUD%2FUeH80S3I9%2BqwvV4D0jUJVCqNn8v1PCJE%3D&h=2793c538\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200917%2FOW6MAMN4IZDIDFXDYWHRKITFLY%2F&h=2f7b3864\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20200917/OW6MAMN4IZDIDFXDYWHRKITFLY/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n尖沙嘴舊樓蝕近五千萬放售<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/KDvoUfryVNsk0w7mgOFvkWXABf4=/640x960/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/AQNNETY7FJG5PHCMBCL2AWRWAA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FKDvoUfryVNsk0w7mgOFvkWXABf4%3D%2F640x960%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FAQNNETY7FJG5PHCMBCL2AWRWAA.jpg&h=4812739c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■太極大樓樓齡約54年，現為一幢12層商住大廈，地下為商舖。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】經濟復蘇無期，有投資者新近蝕約7.6%，放售尖沙嘴太極大樓逾85%業權。<br />\n<br />\n第一太平戴維斯指，尖沙嘴柯士甸道132至134號太極大樓，地盤面積約5,441方呎，可重建總樓面面積65,292方呎。物業樓齡約54年，現為一幢12層商住大廈，地下為商舖；該行是次獲委託出售上述物業36個住宅單位、三個寫字樓單位及一個地舖，涉全幢大廈逾85%業權，業主意向價5.8億元。據了解，業主2018年以6.28億元向「舖王」鄧成波購入上述業權，即最新意向價較兩年前購入價低約4,800萬元或7.6%。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n企業廣場全層7,200萬沽<br />\n<br />\n第一太平戴維斯香港董事總經理及投資部主管袁志光指，新買家可翻新住宅部份作服務式住宅出租，料租金回報達3厘；另亦可申請強拍集齊業權，重建成全新銀座式商廈。<br />\n<br />\n舖市方面，據土地註冊處，。。。。。。。"}]}